  "title": "Quantity Surveyor (LTA Projects) - Roadworks",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a leading player in construction industry. They are looking for a Quantity Surveyor to join their QS Team, in hopes of developing the current high performing team. They are located in the North / East area.</strong></p><p><strong>Duties of Quantity Surveyor:</strong></p><ul><li>Review contracts, measurements, and prepare Bills of Quantities.</li><li>Handle progress claims, variations, and liaise with clients.</li><li>Source and compare quotations, prepare tender pricing.</li><li>Monitor budgets and update management on project matters.</li><li>Verify subcontractor/supplier claims and process payment certifications.</li><li>Attend site and progress meetings, and follow up during the defects liability period.</li><li>Ensure compliance with quality standards and support other tasks as assigned.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min Diploma in Quantity Survey or Civil Engineering</li><li>Min 3 years of Quantity Survey experience in roadwork</li><li>Good negotiation, communication and stakeholder management skills</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><ul><li><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></li><li>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</li><li>EA License No. 19C9682</li><li>EA Reg. No. R22108850 (Chan Mun Mun)</li></ul>",
